						               													<description>The difference between sun and storms is all the difference when fishing. Better check the forecast before you get out on the water! &amp;#10;&amp;#10;This 5-card expansion for Fishing Lessons introduces Weather cards. On any turn in which you replace a card in the Lesson Row from your hand, draw a Weather card and follow its specific placement rules. Each of the 5 unique cards adds a twist to your fishing trip: altered movement, flipped fish, and more!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When a player elects to replace a lesson card in Step 1, they draw a weather card. The weather card is drawn after the lesson card is placed, and is read and activated before Step 2 is resolved. Each weather card is different and has a unique effect on it.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Example card: Sun - The warm water drives some fish deeper. Select a type of fish, and flip all of the cards with that fish face-down.Ignore this effect if all lake cards are face-down already.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
